              "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
              "Text": "_Cultivars used in cropping systems experiments_\n\n(wheat, Base/IniBase)\n\n\n# Wheat\n\nBeckom ~ Gauntlet\n\nBennett\n\nCoolah ~ Gregory\n\nIllabo \n\nKittyhawk\n\nMustang ~ Condo\n\nRaider ~ Lancer\n\nRockstar ~ Gregory/Bolac\n\nScepter\n\n",
