                {
                  "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                  "Text": "This soil file is the master soil file all changes are to be made to this file and then copied to other version of this file \ncurrent version was created on 16 Aug 2019 by Jeremy Whish\nupdated with new condobolin file 30/1/2020 soil from KV created sep2019  soil is based on one developed by John Kirkegaard\nlast updated by Jeremy Whish 7/2/2020\n\nlast updated 8/8/2020 adjustment to lower limit and DUL based on full sampling of all plots layer structure and depth changed to match field ex sampling reduced to 2m \nAll crops have the wheat lowerlimit except mungbeans wheat to 60 then half wheat, then quarter wheat, then 0\nKL Values from apsoil protocol and all soil values from protocol.\n\n30/9/2020  organic carbon finert and fbiom set to apsim standard values",
