                {
                  "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                  "Text": "\nAll crops using wheat LL with mungbean not able to extract water below 150cm\n\nSoil modified and updated by Jeremy Whish on the 7/2/2020\n\nlast updated 17/9/2020 adjustment to lower limit and DUL based on full sampling of all plots layer structure and depth changed to match field ex sampling reduced to 2m \nAll crops have the wheat lowerlimit except mungbeans wheat layer 4 then half wheat, then quarter wheat, then 0\nKL Values from apsoil protocol and all soil values from protocol.\n\n30/9/2020  organic carbon finert and fbiom set to apsim standard values  southrn soil mineralisation turned off",
